channel.title: RSBot is back!
channel.description:
RSBot is back and better then ever, same quality and better just a different spot come check it out!! I have no affiliation with them i just found out about it myself today, im just trying to help spread the word (in which i get nothing for) in hopes to make a strong community.
http://rsbot.info/
Don't just take me word for it, check out the forums:
http://rsbot.info/forum/

Ban him. RSBot.org are the official forums. Advertising a fork pretending to be official is forbidden.

item.title: RSBot is back!
item.dc:creator: @Tenac Tenac
item.description:
@Tenac wrote:

Haha, I can’t express how pathetic PeecsRSBot is to me… Sure RSBot is open sourced GPL, but renaming the bot with no actual improvements and claiming the new one as your own is just pathetic to me. Years of knowledge and experience have been put into the development of RSBot I’m sure and close to none into PeecsBot.

If you want a forum for RSBot, I’d suggest www.qbot2.com which is Qauter’s website, it doesn’t focus 100% around RSBot, but I like Qauters

Read full topic
